metadata.name: Cat #1196
metadata.description: LMC is an extraordinary collection of 1200 uniquely generated Lovely Maniac Cats NFTs by @manisaemi, each possessing its own rarity. Our focus is on building a community and being the first to champion the 1/1 artists community on Foundation. By acquiring these NFTs, you not only become a holder but also gain access to exclusive exhibitions, events in the MetaVerse, and the opportunity to participate in raffles and airdrops of the arts. We are dedicated to supporting artists and growing together, and there are even more thrilling updates to come as we progress on this remarkable journey. If you have a love for both art and cats, seize the opportunity to grab yours now!
